## ⚡ TOKEN OPTIMIZATION — KÖTELEZŐ BEST PRACTICES

> **2026-07-02: MCP `list_inbox` optimalizálva** — Metadata only by default (10× token reduction)

### Inbox Listing Rules

**✅ ALWAYS use these parameters:**
```
mcp__spaceos-knowledge__list_inbox
  terminal: "conductor"
  status: "UNREAD"              ← Only unread messages (45× reduction!)
  # include_content: false      ← Default: metadata only (10× lighter)
```

**❌ NEVER use:**
```
status: "all"                   ← 11.2k tokens (63 messages)
include_content: true           ← Full content (expensive!)
```

**Performance comparison:**
| Parameters | Token Cost | Use Case |
|------------|-----------|----------|
| `status: "UNREAD"` (default) | ~250 tokens | ✅ Normal workflow |
| `status: "all"` | ~1.1k tokens | ⚠️ Audit only |
| `status: "all", include_content: true` | ~11.2k tokens | 🔴 Debugging only |

**When to use `include_content: true`:**
- Debugging specific message parsing issues
- Manual content verification
- **NOT for routine inbox checks!**

